title: Humble Bundle Mojam 2
description:
This torrent contains the "Humble Bundle Mojam 2" games.

Please note that the Humble Bundles are insanely cheap
and if you want to support indie developers and charity
it is well worth spending your money on. The average bundle
comes with a cost of $5 to $6 if you want the extra games.

Visit https://mojang.com/2013/02/mojam-is-over-donate-download-and-play/
for screen-shots and info of the games and developers.

This upload is for the ones who missed it. Since they aren't on steam or another platform.

please visit http://www.humblebundle.com/ for more sales.

This post contains:

Windows:
 - 3918
 - Battle Frogs
 - Endless Nuclear Kittens
 - Low Light Combat
 - Nuclear Pizza War
 - Space Hunk
 - Tektonik
 - Wasteland Kings

Mac OS X:
 - Battle Frogs
 - Endless Nuclear Kittens
 - Low Light Combat
 - Nuclear Pizza War
 - Space Hunk
 - Tektonik

Linux:
 - Battle Frogs
 - Endless Nuclear Kittens
 - Low Light Combat (32 & 64-bit)
 - Nuclear Pizza War (32 & 64-bit)

This post does not contain:
 - source (for developers)
 - extras
